parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the car to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
The failure of the navigation and infotainment system can cause inconvenience and distraction to the driver.
symptoms: and periodic malfunctioning of the system.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights and wiring can cause reduced visibility, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
The failure of the battery can cause the car to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
The failure of the SMG transmission can cause the vehicle to shut down without warning, leading to potential accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks violently when shifting
and may not shift into gear. In some cases
the transmission may fail to engage
causing the vehicle to stall or become immobile.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the hydraulic component can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to loss of power, hesitation, and jerking movements, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle may experience a loud thump or jerk when accelerating from a stop
and the transmission may hesitate to shift into gear.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag warning light may illuminate
and the airbag system may not deploy properly in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The hesitation of the engine can increase the risk of accidents, especially when pulling out into traffic or merging with other vehicles.
symptoms: The engine may hesitate to accelerate
causing the vehicle to slow down or stall.
